  "texts": [
    "Six open-ended questions have been formulated for this purpose, as well as to offer a further complementary answer to the two research questions of the current study.",
    "These are demonstrated in Table 7.",
    "Table 7 clarifies that the interview of respondent teachers deals with certain issues pertinent to the main objective of this study.",
    "These issues revolve around the extent to which virtual learning affects students\" engagement positively and/or negatively, the way virtual learning influences students\" language skills and academic performance, their attendance, and their willingness to communicate.",
    "The results obtained from the interview indicate that respondent teachers expressed positive attitudes concerning the impact of virtual learning on students\" engagement."
  ]
}